{"tid":727781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"考完車pass左後有感，給來緊的學神","createTime":"2018-07-03T09:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T02:23:33.000Z","uid":58266,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"58bbecc6da748d81f1fb028d941222aac369839a","tid":727781,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:33:51.000Z","msg":"之前報左鏗X，阿sir hea左我10堂，我以為錢比公司拆帳，佢唔肯教。跟住再比錢佢學10堂，以為佢袋晒，會肯教。屌佢老母，咪又一撚樣，訓教，睇片，理9你90分鐘係度等車只學6次調頭，咁算，我上網看片再問師兄，諗住自學去考，點知扑佢個街，連考試場地有少少唔同都無撚同我講，肥左。<br />\n跟住望住張滿晒剔的黃紙一度諗，點解可以咁撚不負責任，咁屈機。吹佢唔脹！<br />\n<br />\n所以來緊如果你學車，遇到呢d扑街，記得即刻要求換人。唔好好似我甘諗住自己上網看片再問人攪得掂，我後來換左個肯教的師傅，4堂搞掂晒之前唔啱的野，好多細膩野都提埋你，有d野無人實戰提你真係好易肥。"},{"pid":"b4ba679fe12c30858b23bc00ae13131b57577110","tid":727781,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"考邊區？肯教果個師父有冇contact<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322c644a7d4f3fcde86e3da3c38721f08fa391c3","tid":727781,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ba679fe12c30858b23bc00ae13131b57577110","tid":727781,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"考邊區？肯教果個師父有冇contact<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"考九龍區，有contact，利申：非打手"},{"pid":"8646cdb0e80ff02132690128f797592761556239","tid":727781,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"322c644a7d4f3fcde86e3da3c38721f08fa391c3","tid":727781,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ba679fe12c30858b23bc00ae13131b57577110","tid":727781,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"考邊區？肯教果個師父有冇contact<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"考九龍區，有contact，利申：非打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"咁唔岩了<img src=\"/assets